description: The fund generally will invest at least 80% of its total assets in securities that comprise the underlying index. The underlying index seeks to measure the performance of a portfolio of U.S. dollar-denominated high yield corporate bonds (commonly known as "junk bonds") with maturities or, in some cases, "effective maturities" in the year 2022 (collectively, "2022 Bonds").
name: Invesco BulletShares 2022 High Yield Corporate Bond ETF
